location.fullValue: Gator Trace Golf And Country Club Community

data.description: Don't miss this South Florida resort style home! This home is the Florida dream! Beautifully situated with a view of the lake, this spacious home sets on a golf course, has a heated pool, loaded with upgrades and renovations!   This home also features a new AC, impact windows, working fireplace, a screened lanai around the pool, and a screen enclosure around the upper-deck patio off the master suite for a peaceful view over-looking the golf course.  This home is beautifully landscaped with palm trees and tropical trees and plants! An absolutely breathtaking view! Schedule your private showing today!
